bid(bytes32).notice: Place a blinded bid with `_blindedBid` = keccak256(abi.encodePacked(value, fake, secret)). Setting "fake" to true and sending not the exact amount are ways to hide the real bid but still make the required deposit. The same address can place multiple bids.
